the object {"foo": ["bar", "baz"]} is a well-formatted instance of the schema. The object {"properties": {"foo": ["bar", "baz"]}} is not well-formatted.

Here is the output schema:
```
{"properties": {"answer": {"description": "The corresponding record number surrounded by \"[]\" or \"[0]\" if there is none.", "title": "Answer", "type": "string"}, "explanation": {"description": "A brief explanation of the answer.", "title": "Explanation", "type": "string"}}, "required": ["answer", "explanation"]}
```
